==Daily==
===(Trailblazer), have you seen Stephen?===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Ruan Mei:''' (Trailblazer), have you seen Stephen?
:'''Ruan Mei:''' He's missing, and not even Screwllum and Herta can find him. I bet he must be slacking off somewhere
:'''Ruan Mei:''' I hope he's not asleep
:{Choice} I don't even know what he looks like...
:'''(Trailblazer):''' I don't even know what he looks like...
:'''Ruan Mei:''' Oh, hold on a second
:'''Ruan Mei:''' He took the bait. I found him
:{Choice} That was fast!
:'''(Trailblazer):''' That was fast!
:'''Ruan Mei:''' All the credit goes to the "Stephen Bait"
:'''Ruan Mei:''' Despite the name, it's actually quite simple
:'''Ruan Mei:''' All you need is a piece of fruit cake
:'''Ruan Mei:''' Doesn't matter how much you get. As long as the flavor is right, it will get the job done
:{Choice} Is there a Herta Bait
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Is there a "Herta Bait"!?
::'''Ruan Mei:''' Herta has clear preferences. An interesting Curio should do the trick.
:{Choice} Is there a Screwllum Bait
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Is there a "Screwllum Bait"!?
::'''Ruan Mei:''' Screwllum has always been punctual. The cuff links I prepare for him never come in handy.
:{Choice} Is there a "Ruan Mei Bait"?
:'''(Trailblazer):''' I'm curious about "Ruan Mei Bait" too
:'''Ruan Mei:''' Me?
:'''Ruan Mei:''' Take a guess
:{Choice} Plum blossom cake
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Plum blossom cake?
::'''Ruan Mei:''' More or less
::'''Ruan Mei:''' The aroma of plum blossom cake always brings me back to the time I spent in the lab with my mother when I was little. I loved to show off my work to her at that time
::'''Ruan Mei:''' Instead of bait, I think it's more of a reward to me, which I do miss a lot
:{Choice} Is it... some kinda research?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Is it some kind of research?
::'''Ruan Mei:''' It's human nature to be inquisitive, and all research has a purpose
::'''Ruan Mei:''' But for me, there are only certain kinds of research that are worthy of my attention...
:{Choice} Can I be your bait?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Can I be your bait?
::'''Ruan Mei:''' Alas
::'''Ruan Mei:''' Looks like the Anti-Truth Serum hasn't worn off yet
}}
