===(Trailblazer), you often test...===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Ruan Mei:''' (Trailblazer), you often test the Simulated Universe for Herta, don't you?
:{Choice} I'm not there right now
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Unfortunately, I'm not there right now
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I can make a trip there when I'm free. What's the matter?
:{Choice} I happen to be testing it now
::'''(Trailblazer):''' How serendipitous! I'm testing it now
::'''(Trailblazer):''' What can your "humble assistant" do for you?
:'''Ruan Mei:''' I lost a set of Ruan strings, which should be in Herta's office
:'''Ruan Mei:''' I've got a spare, so there's no rush
:'''Ruan Mei:''' If you happen to stumble on it, please bring it back for me. Thanks in advance
:'''Ruan Mei:''' If Herta asks anything, just tell her I got so mesmerized by her portrait that I forgot about the strings. She shouldn't probe any further
:{Choice} That's so unconvincing
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Sounds unconvincing to me
:{Choice} That's so flattering
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Sounds so flattering
:'''Ruan Mei:''' I'm merely stating facts here
:'''Ruan Mei:''' Herta's beauty is unquestionable, just like her foul temper
:'''Ruan Mei:''' I can't help getting absorbed in the research results whenever I'm at the space station. If I leave something behind, that's the excuse I use, and it always works
:{Choice} You left behind other things before?
:'''(Trailblazer):''' So you left behind other things before?
:'''Ruan Mei:''' I did
:'''Ruan Mei:''' A piece of embroidery, a lifeform nurturing notebook, and the Phase Flame of #29 Sserkal
:{Choice} Embroidery?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Embroidery... You like doing it in your free time, don't you?
::'''Ruan Mei:''' Yes. I made an embroidery of the Blue when I was nearby the railway platform
::'''Ruan Mei:''' It's still missing. Perhaps, some researcher picked it up
::'''Ruan Mei:''' I hope it's in the hands of someone who appreciates it
:{Choice} Lifeform nurturing notebook?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Lifeform nurturing notebook? I think I've seen it somewhere...
::'''Ruan Mei:''' There are researchers who want to duplicate my creations. They do it by circulating poor imitations of my research formulae secretly
::'''Ruan Mei:''' However, the ingredients aren't the key when it comes to nurturing lifeforms
::'''Ruan Mei:''' The most important thing is the spark of inspiration when coming up with the formula
:{Choice} Phase Flame?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Phase Flame? Is Herta aware of it?
::'''Ruan Mei:''' She is. It is just one of many in her collection
::'''Ruan Mei:''' She won't be bothered by it
}}
